name: WestJet Announces Flights to ASIA!
description:
On December 5th, WestJet  made possibly one of the biggest route announcements in their history - flights from Calgary to Tokyo-Narita!

This is WestJet’s first ever flight to Asia, something that had been hotly anticipated ever since they ordered the 787s. Let's see what else they announced today!
